des: Although there are only 16 courses in Alaska, due to the extremely short golf season, the ones you will find there are magnificent. You will find many fine golf courses in picturesque settings with gigantic mountain scenery nearby in or near cities in Alaska, including Fairbanks, Haines, Juneau, Sitka, and Soldotna.
